<msbt attribsize="8">
	<message label="001" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="QuestionMark" target="actor" targetSpec="" />对了，你知道吗？<delay frames="40" />
<anim id="EmotEnd" target="actor" targetSpec="" /><colour id="3" />然然<colour id="65535" />带来的幼苗和种子，<delay20 />
<anim id="Negative" target="actor" targetSpec="" />都是在普通的店里买不到的。<pageBreak /><anim id="Thinking" target="actor" targetSpec="" />那家伙<tag a="110" b="0" /><delay20 />明明一脸呆样，<delay8 />
却只经手稀有的东西，<delay20 />
<anim id="Grin" target="actor" targetSpec="" />没想到这么能干啊。<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="002" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="Explain" target="actor" targetSpec="" />灌木<delay8 />和普通的树不一样，<delay20 />
就算挨着种也不会枯，<delay20 />
<anim id="Nodding" target="actor" targetSpec="" />能好好长起来。<pageBreak /><anim id="AbsentMindedness" target="actor" targetSpec="" />灌木凑成一片<delay8 />
一齐开花的样子，<delay20 />
<anim id="EmotEnd" target="actor" targetSpec="" />那也是相当漂亮的啊。<anim id="FaintSmile" target="actor" targetSpec="" /><tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="003" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="Explain" target="actor" targetSpec="" />这周的地球日啊，<delay20 />
是一场非常重要的活动，<delay8 />专门为了让大家<delay8 />
<anim id="SmugFace" target="actor" targetSpec="" />能够提高爱护花草自然的意识。<pageBreak /><anim id="Eh" target="actor" targetSpec="" />你问我？！<delay frames="40" /><anim id="Confused" target="actor" targetSpec="" />我当然<delay8 />也有在爱护啦。<delay frames="50" />
今天早上也给花浇了很多水<tag a="110" b="0" /><delay frames="40" />
<anim id="TakenAback" target="actor" targetSpec="" /><delay20 />呃！<delay frames="40" /><anim id="Oops" target="actor" targetSpec="" />原来不能浇太多水啊……<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="004" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00">我把花都混种在一起，<delay20 />
<anim id="Shocked" target="actor" targetSpec="" />结果不知道什么时候<delay8 />开出了
没见过的颜色的花。<pageBreak /><anim id="Explain" target="actor" targetSpec="" />于是我不动声色地把那花送给了我妈，<delay20 />
结果她比我预想的还要高兴得多<tag a="110" b="0" /><delay frames="40" />
<anim id="Blushing" target="actor" targetSpec="" />偶尔来一次这样的事也不错啊。<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="005" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="Nodding" target="actor" targetSpec="" />为了改善<tag a="110" b="32" />上的环境，<delay20 />
有什么要帮忙的，记得跟我说。<delay frames="40" />
我是这座<tag a="110" b="32" />上的居民，<anim id="Assent" target="actor" targetSpec="" /><delay20 />可不会吝于帮忙！<pageBreak /><anim id="Smiling" target="actor" targetSpec="" />为了能让这座<tag a="110" b="32" /><delay20 />变成
一座比现在更宜居的<tag a="110" b="32" />，<delay20 />
<anim id="BigSmile" target="actor" targetSpec="" />我们就一起加油吧！<tag a="110" b="6" />。<delay8 /><anim id="FaintSmile" target="actor" targetSpec="" /></message>
</msbt>